157
00:08:20,190 --> 00:08:22,360
It's fine. You don't need to do anything.

158
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,360
Just stay here.

159
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,820
That's the best medicine.

160
00:08:28,870 --> 00:08:29,530
Yi,

161
00:08:30,270 --> 00:08:31,560
take good care of him.

162
00:09:44,470 --> 00:09:45,470
Don't leave.

163
00:09:48,740 --> 00:09:49,550
I won't.

164
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:34,750
Sister.

165
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:35,840
Coming.

166
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:36,550
Sister.

167
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:38,790
Who is it?

168
00:10:40,860 --> 00:10:42,480
How is he? You took him to the hospital?

169
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:43,510
Hospital? No need.

170
00:10:43,510 --> 00:10:45,170
Why are you here, Sister Fang?

171
00:10:45,550 --> 00:10:47,270
He's fine. He is in good hands.

172
00:10:47,660 --> 00:10:49,060
Good hands?

173
00:10:49,510 --> 00:10:50,320
Who?

174
00:10:50,670 --> 00:10:53,080
