175
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,540
Reliable, very reliable.

176
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:56,720
What's not reliable about it?

177
00:10:57,090 --> 00:10:59,180
They're both willing.

178
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:01,080
Don't worry about it.

179
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:05,670
Zhao Hangong, what are you thinking?

180
00:11:06,750 --> 00:11:09,080
They're not together anymore.

181
00:11:09,270 --> 00:11:11,270
Zhou introduced Yi Yi to someone.

182
00:11:11,270 --> 00:11:12,960
They're getting along well.

183
00:11:13,150 --> 00:11:14,600
I'm looking for someone suitable

184
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:15,440
for Wen.

185
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:17,390
Why are you trying to push them together?

186
00:11:17,390 --> 00:11:18,200
I'm not pushing them together.

187
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:19,200
You really have nothing better to do.

188
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,630
They both want this.

189
00:11:20,630 --> 00:11:21,790
Let's not worry about it.

190
00:11:21,790 --> 00:11:22,480
Besides...

191
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:23,740
