194
00:11:26,790 --> 00:11:27,360
That's true.

195
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:28,360
When you first met Jiang,

196
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:29,390
you couldn't even speak.

197
00:11:29,390 --> 00:11:30,510
You kept running to the bathroom.

198
00:11:30,510 --> 00:11:31,840
And you say I don't understand?

199
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:33,750
Stop talking about my embarrassing past.

200
00:11:33,750 --> 00:11:34,600
Alright, Sister.

201
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:35,840
Let's stop worrying about this, okay?

202
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:36,510
Be quiet.

203
00:11:36,910 --> 00:11:38,840
Is this just my personal business?

204
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:39,750
I...

205
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:40,530
Get out!

206
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:42,910
Sister.

207
00:11:43,140 --> 00:11:44,660
Save him some face.

208
00:11:45,630 --> 00:11:46,390
Sister.

209
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:53,850
Come out.

210
00:11:55,910 --> 00:11:56,720
Come out.

211
00:12:04,340 --> 00:12:05,640
Zhao Hangong, go home.

212
00:12:10,980 --> 00:12:11,860
Close the door.

213
00:12:31,390 --> 00:12:33,960
Didn't I make myself clear the other day?

214
00:12:34,510 --> 00:12:36,570
I told you to go home and think it over.

215
00:12:38,150 --> 00:12:39,460
You don't understand

216
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:41,750
what kind of man he is.

217
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:44,370
You two are completely different.

218
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:47,320
Although he used to be an intellectual,

219
00:12:47,790 --> 00:12:49,840
he's been in the army for over ten years.

220
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:52,440
He's been through blood and fire.

221
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:56,270
He's not the bookish scholar you think.

222
00:12:57,270 --> 00:12:59,910
He was once a military commander.

223
00:13:00,630 --> 00:13:02,560
Do you understand what that means?

224
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:06,000
You don't understand at all.

225
00:13:06,510 --> 00:13:07,970
Have you thought about it?

226
00:13:08,170 --> 00:13:09,170
Once you two are together,

227
00:13:09,170 --> 00:13:11,120
what kind of life will you face?

228
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:13,120
Minister Wen is a leader.

229
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:15,320
He will always prioritize his work.

230
00:13:16,270 --> 00:13:17,750
He can't give you romance.

231
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:19,750
He can't give you poetry and art.

232
00:13:19,750 --> 00:13:22,000
And he can't satisfy your fantasies.

233
00:13:22,220 --> 00:13:24,500
