234
00:13:24,530 --> 00:13:26,480
Then what kind of life do I want?

235
00:13:26,620 --> 00:13:27,640
I certainly know.

236
00:13:28,030 --> 00:13:29,440
But I can tell you this.

237
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:32,600
Minister Wen absolutely cannot give you.

238
00:13:32,630 --> 00:13:34,510
I've never expected anyone

239
00:13:34,540 --> 00:13:36,060
to provide the life I want.

240
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:38,340
How do you define your relation with him?

241
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:39,910
I respect Minister Wen.

242
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:42,150
I enjoy talking with him.

243
00:13:42,510 --> 00:13:44,200
Even seeing him, hearing him speak

244
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:46,480
is a sophisticated pleasure.

245
00:13:46,790 --> 00:13:48,320
I won't depend on anyone.

246
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,960
Nor do I ask for anything.

247
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,150
I have my own life.

248
00:13:51,150 --> 00:13:52,510
I have my own work.

249
00:13:52,640 --> 00:13:54,540
Stop beating around the bush. Just say it.

250
00:13:54,540 --> 00:13:56,670
Do you want to form a family with him?

251
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:02,720
Fine.

252
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:05,600
If you insist that I take a stand,

253
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:06,510
I'll tell you.

254
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:10,270
I like Minister Wen.

255
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:13,390
I want to live with him.

256
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:30,120
I want to be with her.

257
00:14:41,030 --> 00:14:41,600
Okay.

258
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:42,730
Alright.

259
00:14:43,670 --> 00:14:45,320
Okay, Wen Pu.

260
00:14:45,670 --> 00:14:46,790
Fine, Wen Pu.

261
00:14:48,270 --> 00:14:50,270
Then we'll follow the regulations.

262
00:14:51,510 --> 00:14:52,670
The organization must conduct

263
00:14:52,670 --> 00:14:54,670
