271
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,550
Please list all your social connections

272
00:16:21,550 --> 00:16:23,080
since you turned eighteen,

273
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:25,360
including relatives, classmates

274
00:16:25,480 --> 00:16:26,410
and colleagues.

275
00:16:26,720 --> 00:16:27,600
Write down clearly

276
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:28,870
their current occupations,

277
00:16:28,870 --> 00:16:29,600
workplaces,

278
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:30,660
and other details.

279
00:16:31,870 --> 00:16:34,080
I lost touch with many people for long.

280
00:16:34,220 --> 00:16:36,000
You just need to provide the list.

281
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,600
We'll investigate the rest.

282
00:16:52,150 --> 00:16:52,950
Minister Wen,

283
00:16:53,270 --> 00:16:55,200
this is my self-criticism report.

284
00:16:55,270 --> 00:16:56,070
Minister Wen,

285
00:16:56,750 --> 00:16:58,280
I've reflected seriously.

286
00:16:58,320 --> 00:16:59,780
I made a terrible mistake.

287
00:17:00,270 --> 00:17:01,030
My mistake was

288
00:17:01,030 --> 00:17:02,680
not reading books or newspapers

289
00:17:02,680 --> 00:17:04,310
and not understanding government policies.

290
00:17:04,310 --> 00:17:05,200
I'm still

291
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:06,640
stuck in old society ways

292
